Path: godot/classes/class_xrfacetracker.rst
Summary: Describes the `blend_shapes` property of XRFaceTracker.

blend_shapes (PackedFloat32Array): The array of face blend shape weights with indices corresponding to the BlendShapeEntry enum. Default: PackedFloat32Array(). Note: The returned array is copied and any changes to it will not update the original property value. See PackedFloat32Array for more details.
---CHUNK---
