Summary: This section describes methods for getting and setting face blend shape weights in XRFaceTracker.

Method: get_blend_shape(blend_shape: BlendShapeEntry) → float
Returns the requested face blend shape weight.

Method: set_blend_shape(blend_shape: BlendShapeEntry, weight: float) → void
Sets a face blend shape weight.